[recv] {"type": "message_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Considering configuration edits**\n\nI’m thinking about whether to change the default assert from simple to repository. It seems to test the configuration effectively since getClasspathLayoutType maps the default to repository. Hm, maybe I should check before I set this — it’s currently using simple, but it might make sense to transition to repository. I'll make sure my edits align with the intended functionality.\n\n**Fixing versioning issues**\n\nThe test is failing because it's expecting version 1.2.3, but I might need a minimal runtime fix to address this. It was probably meant for the initial test of version 3.0.0. I wonder if 3.0.0 was supposed to be a full version. The source indicates that the spec version uses major.minor format, so I need to adjust it to \"1.2\" to maintain the behavior. Let's get this sorted!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0f8abf58aed4ff7a016a26d4cbcd7881938cc0cb004efa4d5c\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqJtTq0KrOPbXhcDqnDUtqSxYnw7quw5hDw1JnTxyLWkyCtKGS-rkWczJY6SKn_KRR7JdIOkcg9vKpGjxipVcwJUhwY3ItzVjeEahZCy_heDCuGkN8aiDK8YIDUmMwALWGPucduQSnNpUoClgRji2jeMOklWx7tiKbLacLvy9AlvNHWiTo1-tBJX3wdJAL4HYyobf1TOOZc1J9RwNz5lKETdQ91DyZhhpJ-_OMUZ68F_rzaV1SPrIeqXFpA9mPcCf6_olHPN5ek6VsGghq8oAxL1dCSORfiFjIYLCt1-SJPdQwFoLa7Lj1k8-yulOZDLaMttnFMjUG1Ly6pTUs4_nUALfWVbEwuQTMx6sM_x2iDj3kLBscLN9kqO184WijsRhEDVQXIVxzEoqFC0GoY3sZtqgXTdHLZ0kO51t94TF4LU85W9ndEROUArWRZeyvfoVxLPOVCgVaV_6mC_EoNO5pvOl88fAQakG6Hs2o0a_yEJa4RKxeWnWdbyhpVwluXQg5OWPH_hAGJQemlapl3jLjfUbE8kIBZz3naIh0kH4bkAgSaqiCRqfxuaV4_LorU5uYt-5RXuAaucd4TmJRQQa9QBVlK90k5_-VbxyicL9qL4V700VPx1GmmP5hw74EhJkvMAoaR6uWZ1u3GEXCwIL4htX3BCiown-y_YlPTz0W3BzPvuy2mke6_a98UnL2Rh51XCc-tJ7jVVMnHAN57SJLQzU5Q1pqTEaj5F4lJJbvfyNNZMz6KpITR7cr1-wr1__LIA9YFiVcYv3IYJYbkT_8pOmR_-mCA6k-CxBzfEKNfCEufnOmfiPpbXmtZXVJFPqmm4fXyZ1ZOd33HuERb4Q90S1GQKmXBAjJBKFZiGOWz_1zEhpzLohozz2prAa9pd07